      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我按这个顺序画：main初始commit → checkout develop → develop第一次commit → checkout main → merge develop → checkout develop → develop第二次commit → checkout main → 最后merge develop。方向用BT（从下往上）比较符合时间线。",
      "elements_involved": [
