      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，BT方向可以。不过确认一下，两次merge develop都是把develop的最新内容合进main，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，两次都是main合并develop。第一次合并后main包含develop的第一个commit，第二次合并后main包含develop的两个commit。develop分支本身保持独立继续开发。",
      "elements_involved": [
